WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.600
I built PolishKey for quick support notes that need to sound clear before you send them.

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:09.600
Highlight the rough text, then press the hotkey or use the right-click Services menu.

00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:14.400
PolishKey rewrites it locally on your Mac, so the draft is not sent to a cloud AI provider.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:19.400
It turns shorthand into a warm reply or a clear internal ticket note.

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:24.400
Try 25 rewrites free. Early users can get a lifetime license for $19.99.
